---
description: Hosted service and worker safety rules
alwaysApply: true
---

For:

background workers  
hosted services  
schedulers  
event dispatchers  
replay services  
webhook runtimes

Rules:

• Always use TenantScopeExecutor
• Never manage tenant scope manually
• Preserve existing cancellation token usage
• Preserve existing logging
• Preserve null-company behavior unless explicitly changed

Before coding:

Explain:

1. Where CompanyId comes from
2. Whether execution is tenant-owned or platform-owned
3. Which executor method will be used
